net.varkhan.base.containers.map
Interface Float2DoubleMap

All Superinterfaces:
Container<Map.Entry<java.lang.Float,java.lang.Double>>, java.lang.Iterable, Map<java.lang.Float,java.lang.Double>, Searchable<java.lang.Float>, Visitable<Map.Entry<java.lang.Float,java.lang.Double>>
public interface Float2DoubleMap
extends Map<java.lang.Float,java.lang.Double>

A searchable container that associates keys to values, and does not allow duplicate keys.

An indexed map of objects, that associates with each unique key an entry, constituted of a modifiable value.
